      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Troubled Waters",
        "Client": "Beautiful Treasure Hunter",
        "Description": "I hunt for ancient treasure that lies\r\nin the deepest rivers and oceans.\r\nSadly, my next diving spot is swim-\r\nming with monsters. Would you\r\nclear them out for me? If you do,\r\nI\u0027ll give you the materials to make\r\nsome new layered armor.",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
